title: Memorandum of Understanding Between Mercosur and the Community of Portuguese Speaking Countries

top_actors.name: Southern Common Market
top_actors.justification: The Southern Common Market (Mercosur) is a key player in the agreement, indicating its central role in the multilateral discussions and initiatives related to trade and cooperation among member countries.

top_actors.name: Community of Portuguese Language Countries
top_actors.justification: The Community of Portuguese Language Countries is significant as it is the other party in the Memorandum of Understanding, highlighting its importance in fostering collaboration and dialogue among Portuguese-speaking nations.

top_themes.name: Bi-regional Cooperation
top_themes.justification: This theme is central to the document as it outlines the collaboration between Mercosur and the Community of Portuguese Speaking Countries, which is the primary focus of the Memorandum of Understanding.
